it’s that time of year again when i revisit my alaska/bagel/lox journey to brush up in time for homemade yom kippur break fast bagels! find the whole video (and the corresponding bagel video!) and recipes on my blog!

@copperriversalmon @spinyourstory

node.text: I had the best and tastiest time hosting the @Boursincheese Wow-liday Cookie Challenge which featured savory cookies created by pastry chefs who I admire so much, @lenasareini, @smallorchids, and @mirouskokovic! Watch the full video here to learn about their cookies and see who won! Then get the recipes at Boursin.com so you can make them at home!! Happy baking :) #ad

node.text: getting ready to make lox for yom kippur and revisiting my bagels and lox project from a few years ago! 🥯🐟 it took me to cordova, alaska, with @copperriversalmon on one of the best most memorable trips of my life. @spinyourstory and i made this fun video about it and you can find the full recipe here http://mynameisyeh.com/mynameisyeh/2017/9/bagels-and-blueberry-lox 🥰❤️🥯🐟 #copperriversalmon #yomkippur

node.text: it's bernie's play kitchen!!!!! i've been dreaming up this tiny kitchen version of our farm kitchen for, well, years (!!) and now here it is just in time to make its debut in the october @foodnetworkmag and on the season 9 premiere episode of #girlmeetsfarm on sunday!! so far bernie has cooked about 12 variations of sprinkle sausage soup for me in this kitchen, each one extremely delish. sources are tagged and a special thank you to @smegusa for the fridge and also to nick for allowing our duvet cover to be cut up and turned into a curtain that would match our kitchen curtains. and don't forget, the october @foodnetworkmag is on newsstands now!

GIVEAWAY! a new school year is BUSY! so my friends at @organicvalley and i want to help take dinner off your plate! one lucky winner will receive a hotdish kit with everything you need to make my easy cheesy garden hotdish, a great jones casserole dish, an autographed copy of #mollyontherange cookbook AND 6 months of @organicvalley products to stock your fridge (total $535 value)!
 
To enter:
follow me and @organicvalley on Instagram, tag a friend in the comments and let me know your favorite hotdish recipe.
 
Giveaway ends 9/22. Open to u.s. residents only. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed, or administered by, or associated with Instagram. One winner will be randomly selected and notified via DM.
 
#backtoschool #weeknightdinners #hotdish #casserolerecipe #mealprep #outsidewithlove #organicvalley

📷: @chantell_lauren

node.text: it’s here! it’s here! the october food network magazine!!! i got to guest edit it and it was a dream come true!!! ❤️ i am sooo excited about the lineup of stories and contributors. there are features on hand-pulled noodles, indian flatbreads, hotdishes (sweet and savory!), black and white cookies, tahini, marzipan, and obviously sprinkles! it is officially on newsstands!!!! also my dad’s in town, say hi 😜😜😜

node.text:
rosh hashanah is nigh and what better tool to cook a honey cake with than an apple spatula?!? to celebrate, i’m giving away five of the apple spatulas that i designed for @williamssonoma @nokidhungry #toolsforchange campaign! 

to enter: comment here with your favorite apple recipe or rosh hashanah recipe and i’ll choose five winners at random later this week! open to u.s. residents. and if you don’t win or are in the market for the matching tea towel, head to the link in profile to get yours :) each one sold provides up to 40 meals for kids in need.

update: this giveaway is now closed! congrats to the winners!
